cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.HC 

The paper deals with sign language recognition using video data, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL). The authors also propose a new architecture for the task, which involves machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper discusses the challenges of collecting and annotating a large-scale dataset, which relates to multimedia (cs.MM) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
